{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897708106,"sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc0810c001OJvisLFF854ZT4","messageID":"msg_d7bc07108001jhvVz5yzl5iQS1","sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_ddb7977eda2a4554b02b0841","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042</path>\n<type>directory</type>\n<entries>\ndelta-spec.md\ndesign.md\nproposal.md\ntasks.md\n\n(4 entries)\n</entries>","metadata":{"preview":"delta-spec.md\ndesign.md\nproposal.md\ntasks.md","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042","time":{"start":1775897708102,"end":1775897708105}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897709621,"sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc086cc0015AwCpgRMWQuoTh","messageID":"msg_d7bc07108001jhvVz5yzl5iQS1","sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_fcbfeaa8eede4098b35cc7ff","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: Define the Go type system for the `CodeInterpreter` Custom Resource Definition in API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`, enabling declarative management of code execution sandbox environments with warm pool support and authentication mode configuration.\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreter CRD type definition\n10: \n11: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreter` as a namespaced Kubernetes custom resource with `Spec` and `Status` subfields, registered in the `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API group.\n12: \n13: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter type is a valid Kubernetes object\n14: - **GIVEN** the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` file exists\n15: - **WHEN** the Go compiler processes the package\n16: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreter` SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`, and implement `runtime.Object` via `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n17: \n18: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter has status subresource enabled\n19: - **GIVEN** the `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker is present on the `CodeInterpreter` type\n20: - **WHEN** `controller-gen crd` generates the CRD YAML\n21: - **THEN** the resulting CRD SHALL include `/status` as a subresource endpoint\n22: \n23: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter is namespaced\n24: - **GIVEN** the `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` marker is present\n25: - **WHEN** the CRD is applied to a cluster\n26: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreter` resources SHALL be scoped to a namespace and require namespace qualification in API requests\n27: \n28: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter displays Age column in kubectl output\n29: - **GIVEN** the `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"` marker is present\n30: - **WHEN** a user runs `kubectl get codeinterpreters`\n31: - **THEN** the output SHALL include an `AGE` column derived from `.metadata.creationTimestamp`\n32: \n33: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterSpec fields\n34: \n35: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterSpec` with fields for port configuration (`Ports`), sandbox template (`Template`), session timeouts (`SessionTimeout`, `MaxSessionDuration`), warm pool sizing (`WarmPoolSize`), and authentication mode (`AuthMode`).\n36: \n37: #### Scenario: Spec uses shared TargetPort type for ports\n38: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterSpec` with `Ports` field\n39: - **WHEN** the type is serialized to JSON\n40: - **THEN** the JSON key SHALL be `ports` (not `targetPort`), and each entry SHALL conform to the shared `TargetPort` struct with `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port`, and `protocol` fields\n41: \n42: #### Scenario: Template uses flat CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate\n43: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterSpec` with `Template` field\n44: - **WHEN** the template is inspected\n45: - **THEN** it SHALL be of type `*CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` with flat fields (`image`, `command`, `args`, `resources`, `environment`, `labels`, `annotations`, `runtimeClassName`, `imagePullPolicy`, `imagePullSecrets`) and SHALL NOT embed `corev1.PodSpec`\n46: \n47: #### Scenario: WarmPoolSize is optional\n48: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterSpec` with `WarmPoolSize` set to `nil`\n49: - **WHEN** the spec is serialized to JSON\n50: - **THEN** the `warmPoolSize` field SHALL be omitted from the output (omitempty behavior)\n51: \n52: #### Scenario: AuthMode defaults to empty string\n53: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterSpec` with `AuthMode` not explicitly set\n54: - **WHEN** the spec is inspected\n55: - **THEN** `AuthMode` SHALL equal `AuthModeType(\"\")` (empty string), not any specific enum value\n56: \n57: #### Scenario: SessionTimeout and MaxSessionDuration use metav1.Duration\n58: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterSpec` with `SessionTimeout` set to 15 minutes\n59: - **WHEN** the spec is serialized to JSON\n60: - **THEN** `sessionTimeout` SHALL render as a duration string (e.g., `\"15m0s\"`) per `metav1.Duration` marshaling\n61: \n62: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterStatus fields\n63: \n64: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterStatus` with `Conditions` (standard Kubernetes condition slice) and `Ready` (boolean readiness indicator).\n65: \n66: #### Scenario: Status includes standard conditions\n67: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterStatus` with conditions\n68: - **WHEN** the status is serialized to JSON\n69: - **THEN** `conditions` SHALL be an array of `metav1.Condition` objects with `type`, `status`, `reason`, `message`, and `lastTransitionTime` fields\n70: \n71: #### Scenario: Ready field indicates operational state\n72: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterStatus` with `Ready: true`\n73: - **WHEN** the status is inspected via client-go\n74: - **THEN** `status.ready` SHALL return `true`, indicating the CodeInterpreter is operational\n75: \n76: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate fields\n77: \n78: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` with flat configuration fields for sandbox pod creation, including image, pull policy, secrets, environment variables, command, arguments, resource requirements, labels, annotations, and runtime class.\n79: \n80: #### Scenario: Template supports custom labels and annotations\n81: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` with `Labels: {\"app\": \"code-interpreter\"}` and `Annotations: {\"agentcube.io/version\": \"1\"}`\n82: - **WHEN** the template is applied to a sandbox pod\n83: - **THEN** the resulting pod SHALL have those labels and annotations propagated\n84: \n85: #### Scenario: Template supports resource requirements\n86: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` with `Resources` set to `corev1.ResourceRequirements{Requests: {\"cpu\": \"1\", \"memory\": \"2Gi\"}}`\n87: - **WHEN** the template is serialized to JSON\n88: - **THEN** `resources` SHALL include `requests` with `cpu` and `memory` values per Kubernetes resource quantity format\n89: \n90: #### Scenario: Template supports runtimeClassName\n91: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` with `RuntimeClassName` set to `\"kuasar-vmm\"`\n92: - **WHEN** the template is serialized to JSON\n93: - **THEN** `runtimeClassName` SHALL be `\"kuasar-vmm\"` in the output\n94: \n95: ### Requirement: AuthModeType and ProtocolType enumerations\n96: \n97: The system SHALL define `AuthModeType` with values `picod` and `none`, and `ProtocolType` with values `HTTP` and `HTTPS`, as typed string constants.\n98: \n99: #### Scenario: AuthModeType constants are valid\n100: - **GIVEN** the constants `AuthModePicoD` and `AuthModeNone` are defined\n101: - **WHEN** their values are inspected\n102: - **THEN** `AuthModePicoD` SHALL equal `\"picod\"` and `AuthModeNone` SHALL equal `\"none\"`\n103: \n104: #### Scenario: ProtocolType constants are valid\n105: - **GIVEN** the constants `ProtocolTypeHTTP` and `ProtocolTypeHTTPS` are defined\n106: - **WHEN** their values are inspected\n107: - **THEN** `ProtocolTypeHTTP` SHALL equal `\"HTTP\"` and `ProtocolTypeHTTPS` SHALL equal `\"HTTPS\"`\n108: \n109: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterList type\n110: \n111: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterList` as a Kubernetes list type containing a slice of `CodeInterpreter` items, registered with the scheme.\n112: \n113: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterList implements runtime.Object\n114: - **GIVEN** the `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object` marker on `CodeInterpreterList`\n115: - **WHEN** the list is passed to a Kubernetes client\n116: - **THEN** it SHALL be accepted as a valid `runtime.Object` for list operations\n117: \n118: #### Scenario: List items are accessible\n119: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreterList` with two items\n120: - **WHEN** the `Items` field is iterated\n121: - **THEN** each item SHALL be a `CodeInterpreter` with fully populated `Spec` and `Status`\n122: \n123: ### Requirement: Scheme registration\n124: \n125: The system SHALL register `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` kinds and their GroupVersionKind constants in `register.go` using the shared `SchemeBuilder`.\n126: \n127: #### Scenario: Kind constants are defined\n128: - **GIVEN** the `register.go` file\n129: - **WHEN** the constants are inspected\n130: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterKind` SHALL equal `\"CodeInterpreter\"`, `CodeInterpreterListKind` SHALL equal `\"CodeInterpreterList\"`, and `CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind` SHALL equal `GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")`\n131: \n132: #### Scenario: Types are registered with the scheme\n133: - **GIVEN** the `init()` function in `codeinterpreter_types.go` calls `SchemeBuilder.Register(&CodeInterpreter{}, &CodeInterpreterList{})`\n134: - **WHEN** the package is imported\n135: - **THEN** both types SHALL be registered in the `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` scheme\n136: \n137: ### Requirement: Shared type reuse\n138: \n139: The system SHALL reuse `TargetPort`, `ProtocolType`, and `AuthModeType` types defined in the same package (shared with AR-001 AgentRuntime) to avoid duplication.\n140: \n141: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter and AgentRuntime share TargetPort\n142: - **GIVEN** both `agent_type.go` and `codeinterpreter_types.go` reference `TargetPort`\n143: - **WHEN** the package is compiled\n144: - **THEN** there SHALL be exactly one definition of `TargetPort` in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` used by both CRD types\n145: \n146: ### Requirement: DeepCopy generation\n147: \n148: The system SHALL generate `DeepCopy`, `DeepCopyInto`, and `DeepCopyObject` methods for all CodeInterpreter types via `controller-gen object`.\n149: \n150: #### Scenario: DeepCopy methods exist for CodeInterpreter\n151: - **GIVEN** `make generate` has been run\n152: - **WHEN** `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` is inspected\n153: - **THEN** it SHALL contain `DeepCopyInto` and `DeepCopy` methods for `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterSpec`, `CodeInterpreterStatus`, `CodeInterpreterList`, and `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: DeepCopy produces independent copies\n156: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreter` with nested `Template.Labels` map\n157: - **WHEN** `DeepCopy()` is called and the copy's labels are modified\n158: - **THEN** the original's labels SHALL remain unchanged (no shared references)\n159: \n160: ### Requirement: Build and test integrity\n161: \n162: The system SHALL compile cleanly and pass all unit tests for the CodeInterpreter types.\n163: \n164: #### Scenario: Package compiles\n165: - **GIVEN** Go toolchain and all dependencies are available\n166: - **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/apis/...` is executed\n167: - **THEN** the command SHALL exit with code 0 and produce no errors\n168: \n169: #### Scenario: Unit tests pass\n170: - **GIVEN** the test file `codeinterpreter_types_test.go` exists\n171: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` is executed\n172: - **THEN** all tests SHALL pass, including enum constant tests, `TargetPort` tests, `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` DeepCopy tests, `CodeInterpreter` DeepCopy tests, and `CodeInterpreterList` DeepCopy tests\n173: \n174: #### Scenario: Generated code is up to date\n175: - **GIVEN** `make generate` has been run after type changes\n176: - **WHEN** `git diff --exit-code` is checked on `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n177: - **THEN** there SHALL be no uncommitted changes (generated code matches source types)\n\n(End of file - total 177 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefine the Go type system for the `CodeInterpreter` Custom Resource Definition in API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`, enabling declarative management of code execution sandbox environments with warm pool support and authentication mode configuration.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: CodeInterpreter CRD type definition\n\nThe system SHALL define `CodeInterpreter` as a namespaced Kubernetes custom resource with `Spec` and `Status` subfields, registered in the `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API group.\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreter type is a valid Kubernetes object\n- **GIVEN** the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` file exists\n- **WHEN** the Go compiler processes the package\n- **THEN** `CodeInterpreter` SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`, and implement `runtime.Object` via `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n\n#### Scenario: CodeInterpreter has status subresource enabled\n- **GIVEN** the `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker is present on the `CodeInterpreter` type\n- **WHEN** `controller-gen crd` generates the CRD YAML","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775897709612,"end":1775897709620}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897710972,"sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc08cbc001Etb5WYTGN8HoM2","messageID":"msg_d7bc07108001jhvVz5yzl5iQS1","sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_a3a85e5edc4740cbacc199f7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-010: Router 会话管理 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 `pkg/router` 模块实现完整的会话管理能力，在 AR-009（HTTP 反向代理核心）的基础上，扩展 SessionManager 接口、实现 Redis/Valkey Store 后端、激活 Informer 事件处理器、引入会话生命周期 GC，并增强代理流程的会话感知能力。本变更是对 AR-007（Reconciler 控制器）的下游消费方，同时依赖 session-store spec 中定义的存储契约。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: SessionManager 接口扩展\n10: \n11: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/session_manager.go` 中扩展 `SessionManager` 接口，新增以下方法：\n12: \n13: ```go\n14: type SessionManager interface {\n15:     // 现有方法（AR-009）\n16:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n17: \n18:     // 新增方法（AR-010）\n19:     CreateSession(ctx context.Context, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n20:     UpdateSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n21:     DeleteSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n22:     UpdateLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n23:     ListSessions(ctx context.Context) (map[string]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n24: }\n25: ```\n26: \n27: `CreateSession` SHALL 调用 `store.StoreSandbox` 将会话元数据写入存储后端。\n28: \n29: `UpdateSession` SHALL 调用 `store.UpdateSandbox` 更新已存在会话的元数据。\n30: \n31: `DeleteSession` SHALL 调用 `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 删除会话及关联索引。\n32: \n33: `UpdateLastActivity` SHALL 调用 `store.UpdateSessionLastActivity` 更新最后活跃时间。\n34: \n35: `ListSessions` SHALL 调用 `store.ListSandboxes` 返回所有活跃会话。\n36: \n37: #### Scenario: CreateSession 写入存储\n38: \n39: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo{SessionID: \"sess-001\", SandboxName: \"my-runtime-abc\", Kind: \"AgentRuntime\"}`\n40: - **WHEN** `CreateSession(ctx, info)` 被调用\n41: - **THEN** `store.StoreSandbox(ctx, \"sess-001\", info)` 被调用且返回 nil\n42: \n43: #### Scenario: UpdateSession 更新已存在会话\n44: \n45: - **GIVEN** 存储中存在 `sess-001` 条目\n46: - **WHEN** `UpdateSession(ctx, \"sess-001\", updatedInfo)` 被调用\n47: - **THEN** `store.UpdateSandbox(ctx, \"sess-001\", updatedInfo)` 被调用\n48: \n49: #### Scenario: DeleteSession 清理会话\n50: \n51: - **GIVEN** 存储中存在 `sess-001` 条目\n52: - **WHEN** `DeleteSession(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 被调用\n53: - **THEN** `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 被调用\n54: \n55: #### Scenario: UpdateLastActivity 更新活跃时间\n56: \n57: - **GIVEN** 存储中存在 `sess-001` 条目\n58: - **WHEN** `UpdateLastActivity(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 被调用\n59: - **THEN** `store.UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"sess-001\", time.Now())` 被调用\n60: \n61: #### Scenario: ListSessions 返回所有会话\n62: \n63: - **GIVEN** 存储中存在 `sess-001` 和 `sess-002` 条目\n64: - **WHEN** `ListSessions(ctx)` 被调用\n65: - **THEN** 返回包含两个条目的 map，key 为 sessionID\n66: \n67: ---\n68: \n69: ### Requirement: Redis/Valkey Store 实现\n70: \n71: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/store/` 下实现 Redis 和 Valkey 两种后端，满足 session-store spec 中定义的契约：\n72: \n73: **接口契约：**\n74: \n75: | 方法 | 行为 |\n76: |------|------|\n77: | `StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID, info)` | SETNX session key + ZADD expiry + ZADD last_activity（原子管道） |\n78: | `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sessionID, info)` | SET XX（仅更新已存在的 key，不修改 ZSET） |\n79: | `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)` | DEL session key + ZREM expiry + ZREM last_activity（原子管道） |\n80: | `GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)` | GET session key，不存在返回 `ErrNotFound` |\n81: | `ListSandboxes(ctx)` | 遍历 `session:expiry` ZSET 加载所有会话 |\n82: | `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, at)` | 验证 session key 存在后 ZADD last_activity |\n83: \n84: **Key 命名规范：**\n85: - 主键：`session:{sessionID}`（JSON 文档）\n86: - 过期索引：`session:expiry`（sorted set，score = ExpiresAt Unix 秒）\n87: - 活跃索引：`session:last_activity`（sorted set，score = last activity Unix 秒）\n88: \n89: **Provider 选择：**\n90: - 环境变量 `STORE_TYPE`（大小写不敏感），未设置时默认 `redis`\n91: - 支持值：`redis`、`valkey`，其他值初始化失败\n92: \n93: **Redis 配置：**\n94: - 必需：`REDIS_ADDR`\n95: - 默认要求密码：`REDIS_PASSWORD` 非空，除非 `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`\n96: \n97: **Valkey 配置：**\n98: - 必需：`VALKEY_ADDR`（逗号分隔，split 为 `InitAddress`）\n99: - 默认要求密码：`VALKEY_PASSWORD` 非空，除非 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`\n100: - 可选：`VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE=true` → `DisableCache`，`VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE=true` → `ForceSingleClient`\n101: \n102: **单例访问：**\n103: - `Storage()` 使用 `sync.Once` 初始化\n104: - 初始化失败时通过 `klog.Fatal` 记录\n105: \n106: #### Scenario: 默认 Provider 为 Redis\n107: \n108: - **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE` 未设置\n109: - **WHEN** `Storage()` 首次调用\n110: - **THEN** 构造 Redis 实现\n111: \n112: #### Scenario: 主键命名\n113: \n114: - **GIVEN** sessionID 为 `abc`\n115: - **WHEN** Store 写入会话数据\n116: - **THEN** Redis key 为 `session:abc`\n117: \n118: #### Scenario: 过期索引 ZADD\n119: \n120: - **GIVEN** SandboxInfo 的 ExpiresAt 为 `2026-04-10T10:00:00Z`（Unix 秒 1744279200）\n121: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` 执行\n122: - **THEN** `session:expiry` ZSET 中 member `abc` 的 score 为 `1744279200`\n123: \n124: #### Scenario: 活跃索引 ZADD\n125: \n126: - **GIVEN** 当前时间为 `2026-04-10T09:00:00Z`（Unix 秒 1744275600）\n127: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` 执行\n128: - **THEN** `session:last_activity` ZSET 中 member `abc` 的 score 为 `1744275600`\n129: \n130: #### Scenario: 获取不存在的会话返回 ErrNotFound\n131: \n132: - **GIVEN** `session:unknown` key 不存在\n133: - **WHEN** `GetSandbox(ctx, \"unknown\")` 被调用\n134: - **THEN** 返回 `ErrNotFound`\n135: \n136: #### Scenario: nil Sandbox 被拒绝\n137: \n138: - **GIVEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, \"sess-001\", nil)`\n139: - **WHEN** 被调用\n140: - **THEN** 返回错误，指示 sandbox 为 nil\n141: \n142: #### Scenario: UpdateSandbox 对不存在的 key 返回错误\n143: \n144: - **GIVEN** `session:unknown` key 不存在\n145: - **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, \"unknown\", info)` 被调用\n146: - **THEN** 返回错误（Redis: SET XX 返回 false → `key not exists`）\n147: \n148: #### Scenario: 删除操作清理所有关联 key\n149: \n150: - **GIVEN** 会话 `sess-001` 存在于主键和两个 ZSET 中\n151: - **WHEN** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 执行成功\n152: - **THEN** `GET session:sess-001` 返回 nil，两个 ZSET 中均不包含 `sess-001`\n153: \n154: #### Scenario: Valkey 多地址解析\n155: \n156: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR = \"valkey1:6379,valkey2:6379,valkey3:6379\"`\n157: - **WHEN** Valkey Store 初始化\n158: - **THEN** `InitAddress` 包含三个地址\n159: \n160: #### Scenario: 不支持的 STORE_TYPE 初始化失败\n161: \n162: - **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE = \"memcached\"`\n163: - **WHEN** `Storage()` 首次调用\n164: - **THEN** 初始化失败，记录 fatal 日志\n165: \n166: #### Scenario: 并发调用 Storage() 仅初始化一次\n167: \n168: - **GIVEN** 多个 goroutine 同时调用 `Storage()`\n169: - **WHEN** 执行完成\n170: - **THEN** `initStore` 仅执行一次，所有调用返回同一实例\n171: \n172: ---\n173: \n174: ### Requirement: StoreSandbox 原子性\n175: \n176: The system SHALL 在 `StoreSandbox` 中使用 Redis pipeline 或 Valkey multi block 确保以下操作的原子性：\n177: 1. SETNX `session:{sessionID}` 写入 JSON 文档\n178: 2. ZADD `session:expiry` 添加过期索引\n179: 3. ZADD `session:last_activity` 添加活跃索引\n180: \n181: 若管道中任一命令失败，整个操作 SHALL 失败，不产生部分写入。\n182: \n183: #### Scenario: 原子写入成功\n184: \n185: - **GIVEN** Redis/Valkey 连接正常\n186: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, \"sess-001\", validInfo)` 被调用\n187: - **THEN** 三个命令在一个管道中执行，全部成功\n188: \n189: #### Scenario: 原子写入部分失败回滚\n190: \n191: - **GIVEN** Redis/Valkey 在管道执行过程中断开连接\n192: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` 执行\n193: - **THEN** 返回错误，不产生部分写入（SETNX 未执行则 ZSET 不写入）\n194: \n195: ---\n196: \n197: ### Requirement: UpdateSessionLastActivity 前置检查\n198: \n199: The system SHALL 在 `UpdateSessionLastActivity` 中执行以下检查：\n200: 1. 若 `sessionID` 为空，返回错误\n201: 2. 若 `at` 为零时间（`time.IsZero()`），使用 `time.Now()`\n202: 3. 验证 `session:{sessionID}` key 存在，不存在返回 `ErrNotFound`\n203: 4. 执行 ZADD `session:last_activity` 更新活跃索引\n204: \n205: #### Scenario: 空 sessionID 被拒绝\n206: \n207: - **GIVEN** `sessionID = \"\"`\n208: - **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"\", time.Now())` 被调用\n209: - **THEN** 返回错误\n210: \n211: #### Scenario: 零时间自动使用当前时间\n212: \n213: - **GIVEN** `at = time.Time{}`（零时间）\n214: - **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"sess-001\", at)` 被调用\n215: - **THEN** 使用 `time.Now()` 作为 score\n216: \n217: #### Scenario: 未知会话的活跃时间更新\n218: \n219: - **GIVEN** `session:sess-unknown` key 不存在\n220: - **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"sess-unknown\", time.Now())` 被调用\n221: - **THEN** 返回 `ErrNotFound`\n222: \n223: ---\n224: \n225: ### Requirement: ListExpiredSandboxes 与 ListInactiveSandboxes\n226: \n227: The system SHALL 在 Store 接口中新增以下方法（供 GC 使用）：\n228: \n229: ```go\n230: ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n231: ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n232: ```\n233: \n234: `ListExpiredSandboxes` SHALL 使用 `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:expiry -inf <before.Unix()> LIMIT 0 <limit>` 查询过期会话 ID，然后批量加载 JSON 文档。\n235: \n236: `ListInactiveSandboxes` SHALL 使用 `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:last_activity -inf <before.Unix()> LIMIT 0 <limit>` 查询不活跃会话 ID，然后批量加载 JSON 文档。\n237: \n238: 加载 JSON 时若某个 session ID 对应的主键不存在（孤立 ZSET 成员），SHALL 跳过该条目而不使整个批次失败。\n239: \n240: #### Scenario: 查询过期会话\n241: \n242: - **GIVEN** `session:expiry` 中有 `sess-001`（score=1000）和 `sess-002`（score=2000）\n243: - **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, time.Unix(1500, 0), 10)` 被调用\n244: - **THEN** 返回 `sess-001` 的 SandboxInfo，不包含 `sess-002`\n245: \n246: #### Scenario: 孤立 ZSET 成员被跳过\n247: \n248: - **GIVEN** `session:expiry` 中有 `sess-orphan`，但 `session:sess-orphan` key 不存在\n249: - **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes` 执行\n250: - **THEN** `sess-orphan` 被跳过，不返回错误\n251: \n252: ---\n253: \n254: ### Requirement: Informer 事件处理器激活\n255: \n256: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/informer.go` 中将 Informer 事件处理器从 stub 改为实际更新会话缓存和路由表：\n257: \n258: **AgentRuntime 事件处理：**\n259: \n260: | 事件 | 行为 |\n261: |------|------|\n262: | `AddFunc` | 从 CR labels 提取 `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id`，构建 `SandboxInfo`，调用 `router.AddRoute` 注册路由 |\n263: | `UpdateFunc` | 比较新旧 CR 的 `status.conditions`，若 `Ready` 条件变更，调用 `store.UpdateSandbox` 更新会话状态 |\n264: | `DeleteFunc` | 从 CR labels 或 tombstone 提取 session-id，调用 `router.RemoveRoute` 和 `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID` |\n265: \n266: **CodeInterpreter 事件处理：**\n267: \n268: | 事件 | 行为 |\n269: |------|------|\n270: | `AddFunc` | 同 AgentRuntime AddFunc，Kind 标识为 `CodeInterpreter` |\n271: | `UpdateFunc` | 同 AgentRuntime UpdateFunc，额外处理 Warm Pool 激活事件（`spec.warmPoolSize` 从 0 变为 >0） |\n272: | `DeleteFunc` | 同 AgentRuntime DeleteFunc |\n273: \n274: **Label 提取：**\n275: - `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id` → `SandboxInfo.SessionID`\n276: - `runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name` → `SandboxInfo.SandboxName`\n277: - `runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name` → `SandboxInfo.WorkloadName`\n278: \n279: **状态映射（CR conditions → Store status）：**\n280: \n281: | Ready Condition | Store Status |\n282: |-----------------|--------------|\n283: | 缺失             | `pending`    |\n284: | `status: Unknown` | `pending`    |\n285: | `status: True`   | `running`    |\n286: | `status: False`, `reason: Terminated` | `terminated` |\n287: | `status: False`, 其他 reason | `pending` |\n288: \n289: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 新增时注册路由\n290: \n291: - **GIVEN** 新的 AgentRuntime CR `default/my-runtime`，labels 包含 `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id: sess-001`\n292: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeAdded` 被触发\n293: - **THEN** 构建 `SandboxInfo{SessionID: \"sess-001\", Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Status: \"pending\"}`\n294: - **AND** `router.AddRoute` 被调用注册对应路由\n295: \n296: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 状态从 Pending 变为 Running\n297: \n298: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR 的 `status.conditions` 中 `Ready` 条件从缺失变为 `True`\n299: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeUpdated` 被触发\n300: - **THEN** `store.UpdateSandbox` 被调用，将会话状态更新为 `running`\n301: \n302: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 删除时清理路由和存储\n303: \n304: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR `default/my-runtime` 被删除，labels 包含 `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id: sess-001`\n305: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeDeleted` 被触发\n306: - **THEN** `router.RemoveRoute` 被调用移除路由\n307: - **AND** `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 被调用\n308: \n309: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter Warm Pool 激活\n310: \n311: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter CR 的 `spec.warmPoolSize` 从 0 变为 5\n312: - **WHEN** `onCodeInterpreterUpdated` 被触发\n313: - **THEN** 记录 Warm Pool 激活日志，包含 pool size 值\n314: \n315: #### Scenario: Tombstone 处理\n316: \n317: - **GIVEN** informer 在缓存未同步时收到删除事件，obj 为 `cache.DeletedFinalStateUnknown`\n318: - **WHEN** `DeleteFunc` 被触发\n319: - **THEN** 从 `DeletedFinalStateUnknown.Obj` 提取对象并生成 session-id\n320: \n321: #### Scenario: 无 session-id label 的 CR 被忽略\n322: \n323: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR 无 `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id` label\n324: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeAdded` 被触发\n325: - **THEN** 记录警告日志，不执行 Store 或 Router 操作\n326: \n327: ---\n328: \n329: ### Requirement: 会话生命周期 GC\n330: \n331: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/session_lifecycle.go` 中实现 `LifecycleManager`：\n332: \n333: ```go\n334: type LifecycleManager struct {\n335:     store         store.Store\n336:     checkInterval time.Duration\n337:     idleTimeout   time.Duration\n338:     maxDuration   time.Duration\n339:     clientset     clientset.Interface\n340: }\n341: ```\n342: \n343: `Start(ctx)` SHALL 启动后台 GC 协程，按 `checkInterval` 周期执行以下清理：\n344: \n345: 1. **TTL 过期清理（cleanupExpired）**：调用 `store.ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, time.Now(), batchSize)`，对每个过期会话调用 `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID`\n346: 2. **空闲超时清理（cleanupIdle）**：调用 `store.ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, time.Now().Add(-idleTimeout), batchSize)`，对每个不活跃会话调用 `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID`\n347: 3. **孤儿 CR 清理（cleanupOrphans）**：遍历 `store.ListSandboxes` 中的会话，通过 Lister 验证对应 CR 是否存在，若 CR 不存在则清理 Store 条目\n348: 4. **幽灵条目清理（cleanupGhosts）**：通过 Lister 列出所有 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CR，验证 Store 中是否有对应条目，若 Store 中缺失则补建\n349: \n350: `Stop()` SHALL 发送停止信号并等待 GC 协程退出（超时 10 秒）。\n351: \n352: **默认配置：**\n353: - `checkInterval`: 5 分钟\n354: - `idleTimeout`: 30 分钟（可被 CR 的 `spec.sessionTimeout` 覆盖）\n355: - `maxDuration`: 24 小时（可被 CR 的 `spec.maxSessionDuration` 覆盖）\n356: - `batchSize`: 100\n357: \n358: #### Scenario: TTL 过期会话被清理\n359: \n360: - **GIVEN** 会话 `sess-001` 的 ExpiresAt 已过\n361: - **WHEN** GC 周期执行 `cleanupExpired`\n362: - **THEN** `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 被调用\n363: \n364: #### Scenario: 空闲超时会话被清理\n365: \n366: - **GIVEN** 会话 `sess-002` 的 LastActivityAt 为 35 分钟前，idleTimeout 为 30 分钟\n367: - **WHEN** GC 周期执行 `cleanupIdle`\n368: - **THEN** `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-002\")` 被调用\n369: \n370: #### Scenario: 孤儿 CR 条目被清理\n371: \n372: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 `sess-003`，但对应 AgentRuntime CR 已被删除\n373: - **WHEN** GC 周期执行 `cleanupOrphans`\n374: - **THEN** `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-003\")` 被调用\n375: \n376: #### Scenario: 幽灵条目被补建\n377: \n378: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR `default/my-runtime` 存在且携带 session-id，但 Store 中无对应条目\n379: - **WHEN** GC 周期执行 `cleanupGhosts`\n380: - **THEN** `store.StoreSandbox` 被调用补建会话条目\n381: \n382: #### Scenario: GC 协程优雅停止\n383: \n384: - **GIVEN** GC 协程正在运行\n385: - **WHEN** `Stop()` 被调用\n386: - **THEN** GC 协程在 10 秒内退出\n387: \n388: #### Scenario: Store 不可用时 GC 不 panic\n389: \n390: - **GIVEN** Redis/Valkey 连接断开\n391: - **WHEN** GC 周期执行\n392: - **THEN** 记录错误日志，不 panic，下个周期重试\n393: \n394: ---\n395: \n396: ### Requirement: 代理流程会话感知增强\n397: \n398: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/proxy.go` 中增强代理逻辑：\n399: \n400: **成功路径（两次 LastActivityAt 更新）：**\n401: 1. 解析 session ID 后调用 `UpdateLastActivity(ctx, sessionID)`（第一次）\n402: 2. 执行 `forwardToSandbox` 反向代理\n403: 3. 代理成功后再次调用 `UpdateLastActivity(ctx, sessionID)`（第二次）\n404: \n405: **错误处理：**\n406: - `UpdateLastActivity` 失败 SHALL 仅记录 warning 日志，不阻断代理流程\n407: - 会话状态为 `terminated` 时，代理请求 SHALL 返回 410 Gone `{\"error\":\"session has been terminated\"}`\n408: \n409: **JWT 注入增强：**\n410: - 对于 Sandbox/SandboxClaim kind 的入口点，在代理前生成 JWT 并注入 `Authorization: Bearer <token>`\n411: - JWT 签名失败 SHALL 返回 500 `{\"code\":\"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\",\"error\":\"failed to sign request\"}`\n412: \n413: **响应头注入：**\n414: - 所有代理响应 SHALL 携带 `x-agentcube-session-id` header，值为解析后的 session ID\n415: \n416: #### Scenario: 成功路径调用两次 UpdateLastActivity\n417: \n418: - **GIVEN** session ID 为 `sess-001`，sandbox 解析成功且代理转发成功\n419: - **WHEN** invoke handler 完成\n420: - **THEN** `UpdateLastActivity` 被调用两次（解析后和转发后）\n421: \n422: #### Scenario: LastActivity 更新失败不阻断代理\n423: \n424: - **GIVEN** `UpdateLastActivity` 返回错误（Store 不可用）\n425: - **WHEN** sandbox 解析成功\n426: - **THEN** 代理仍然执行，错误仅被记录为 warning\n427: \n428: #### Scenario: 已终止会话返回 410\n429: \n430: - **GIVEN** 会话 `sess-001` 的 Status 为 `terminated`\n431: - **WHEN** 代理请求到达\n432: - **THEN** 响应 410，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"session has been terminated\"}`\n433: \n434: #### Scenario: 代理响应携带 session ID header\n435: \n436: - **GIVEN** session ID 为 `sess-001`\n437: - **WHEN** 代理响应返回\n438: - **THEN** 响应 header 包含 `x-agentcube-session-id: sess-001`\n439: \n440: ---\n441: \n442: ### Requirement: SessionManager 与 Store 集成\n443: \n444: The system SHALL 在 `NewSessionManager` 中注入 Store 实例：\n445: \n446: ```go\n447: func NewSessionManager(storeClient store.Store) (SessionManager, error)\n448: ```\n449: \n450: `GetSandboxBySession` 的会话解析流程 SHALL：\n451: 1. 若 `sessionID` 非空：调用 `storeClient.GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)` 获取 `SandboxInfo`\n452: 2. 若 Store 返回 `ErrNotFound`：返回 `NewSessionNotFoundError(sessionID)`\n453: 3. 若 `sessionID` 为空：POST 到 WorkloadManager 创建 sandbox（AR-009 已有逻辑）\n454: 4. 创建成功后调用 `CreateSession(ctx, newInfo)` 写入 Store\n455: \n456: #### Scenario: 创建沙箱后写入 Store\n457: \n458: - **GIVEN** 空 sessionID，WorkloadManager 创建成功返回 `CreateSandboxResponse{SessionID: \"sess-new\", ...}`\n459: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession(ctx, \"\", \"default\", \"my-runtime\", \"AgentRuntime\")` 被调用\n460: - **THEN** 构建 `SandboxInfo`\n461: - **AND** `CreateSession(ctx, newInfo)` 被调用写入 Store\n462: \n463: #### Scenario: 已知 sessionID 从 Store 获取\n464: \n465: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 `sess-001` 条目\n466: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession(ctx, \"sess-001\", \"default\", \"my-runtime\", \"AgentRuntime\")` 被调用\n467: - **THEN** 返回对应的 `*types.SandboxInfo`\n468: \n469: ---\n470: \n471: ### Requirement: Server 集成会话管理组件\n472: \n473: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/server.go` 中扩展 `Server` 结构体，新增以下字段：\n474: \n475: ```go\n476: type Server struct {\n477:     // 现有字段（AR-009）\n478:     config         *Config\n479:     engine         *gin.Engine\n480:     httpServer     *http.Server\n481:     sessionManager SessionManager\n482:     storeClient    store.Store\n483:     httpTransport  *http.Transport\n484:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n485: \n486:     // 新增字段（AR-010）\n487:     informerManager *InformerManager\n488:     lifecycleManager *LifecycleManager\n489: }\n490: ```\n491: \n492: `NewServer` SHALL 在构造函数中：\n493: 1. 初始化 `store.Store` 实例（通过 `store.Storage()`）\n494: 2. 构造 `InformerManager` 并传入 `router` 引用\n495: 3. 构造 `LifecycleManager` 并传入 `store` 和 `clientset`\n496: 4. 注册路由（含 informer 和 lifecycle 组件）\n497: \n498: `Start()` SHALL 在 HTTP 服务器启动前：\n499: 1. 启动 `InformerManager`（`im.Start(stopCh)`）\n500: 2. 启动 `LifecycleManager`（`lm.Start(ctx)`）\n501: \n502: `Shutdown(ctx)` SHALL 按以下顺序执行：\n503: 1. 停止 `LifecycleManager`\n504: 2. 停止 `InformerManager`\n505: 3. 优雅关闭 HTTP 服务器\n506: \n507: #### Scenario: Server 启动时 Informer 和 GC 同时运行\n508: \n509: - **GIVEN** `NewServer` 构造完成\n510: - **WHEN** `Start()` 被调用\n511: - **THEN** `InformerManager.Start` 和 `LifecycleManager.Start` 在 HTTP 服务器监听前被调用\n512: \n513: #### Scenario: Server 关闭时按序停止组件\n514: \n515: - **GIVEN** Server 正在运行\n516: - **WHEN** `Shutdown(ctx)` 被调用\n517: - **THEN** `LifecycleManager.Stop` 先执行，然后 `InformerManager` 停止，最后 HTTP 服务器关闭\n518: \n519: ---\n520: \n521: ### Requirement: Config 扩展会话相关配置\n522: \n523: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/config.go` 中扩展 `Config` 结构体，新增以下字段：\n524: \n525: | 字段 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n526: |------|------|--------|------|\n527: | `SessionCheckInterval time.Duration` | `time.Duration` | `5 * time.Minute` | GC 检查间隔 |\n528: | `SessionIdleTimeout time.Duration` | `time.Duration` | `30 * time.Minute` | 空闲超时 |\n529: | `SessionMaxDuration time.Duration` | `time.Duration` | `24 * time.Hour` | 最大会话时长 |\n530: | `StoreType string` | `string` | `\"\"`（使用环境变量） | 存储类型（redis/valkey） |\n531: \n532: CLI 标志 SHALL 支持：\n533: \n534: | Flag | 类型 | 默认值 |\n535: |------|------|--------|\n536: | `-session-check-interval` | duration | `5m` |\n537: | `-session-idle-timeout` | duration | `30m` |\n538: | `-session-max-duration` | duration | `24h` |\n539: | `-store-type` | string | `\"\"` |\n540: \n541: #### Scenario: 默认会话配置\n542: \n543: - **GIVEN** 未传入会话相关 CLI 标志\n544: - **WHEN** `NewDefaultConfig()` 被调用\n545: - **THEN** `SessionCheckInterval = 5m`，`SessionIdleTimeout = 30m`，`SessionMaxDuration = 24h`\n546: \n547: #### Scenario: 自定义会话超时\n548: \n549: - **GIVEN** CLI 标志 `-session-idle-timeout=1h -session-max-duration=48h`\n550: - **WHEN** `main()` 解析标志\n551: - **THEN** `Config.SessionIdleTimeout = 1h`，`Config.SessionMaxDuration = 48h`\n552: \n553: ---\n554: \n555: ### Requirement: 编译与测试门禁\n556: \n557: The system SHALL 满足以下门禁：\n558: 1. `go build ./pkg/router/...` 编译通过\n559: 2. `go build ./pkg/store/...` 编译通过\n560: 3. `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` 全部通过\n561: 4. `go test ./pkg/store/... -v` 全部通过\n562: 5. `go test -race ./pkg/router/...` 无 data race 告警\n563: 6. `go test -race ./pkg/store/...` 无 data race 告警\n564: 7. 无 `log.Printf` 残留（使用 `slog` 或 `klog`）\n565: \n566: #### Scenario: pkg/router 编译通过\n567: \n568: - **GIVEN** 所有 router 代码已编写完成\n569: - **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/router/...` 执行\n570: - **THEN** 无编译错误\n571: \n572: #### Scenario: pkg/store 编译通过\n573: \n574: - **GIVEN** 所有 store 代码已编写完成\n575: - **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/store/...` 执行\n576: - **THEN** 无编译错误\n577: \n578: #### Scenario: 所有单元测试通过\n579: \n580: - **GIVEN** 测试用例已编写（含 SessionManager、Store、Informer、LifecycleManager）\n581: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/router/... ./pkg/store/... -v` 执行\n582: - **THEN** 所有测试通过\n583: \n584: #### Scenario: Race detector 无告警\n585: \n586: - **GIVEN** 并发场景测试已覆盖（Store 原子操作、Informer 回调、GC 协程）\n587: - **WHEN** `go test -race ./pkg/router/... ./pkg/store/...` 执行\n588: - **THEN** 无 data race 告警\n589: \n590: #### Scenario: 无 log.Printf 残留\n591: \n592: - **GIVEN** 所有日志已使用 `slog` 或 `klog`\n593: - **WHEN** `grep -rn 'log\\.Printf' pkg/router/ pkg/store/` 执行\n594: - **THEN** 无匹配结果\n\n(End of file - total 594 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-010: Router 会话管理 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 `pkg/router` 模块实现完整的会话管理能力，在 AR-009（HTTP 反向代理核心）的基础上，扩展 SessionManager 接口、实现 Redis/Valkey Store 后端、激活 Informer 事件处理器、引入会话生命周期 GC，并增强代理流程的会话感知能力。本变更是对 AR-007（Reconciler 控制器）的下游消费方，同时依赖 session-store spec 中定义的存储契约。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: SessionManager 接口扩展\n\nThe system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/session_manager.go` 中扩展 `SessionManager` 接口，新增以下方法：\n\n```go\ntype SessionManager interface {\n    // 现有方法（AR-009）\n    GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n\n    // 新增方法（AR-010）\n    CreateSession(ctx context.Context, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n    UpdateSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *types.SandboxInfo) error","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775897710952,"end":1775897710970}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775897711039,"sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc091b1001ZJ7zJlvV5W5Ayb","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7bc07108001jhvVz5yzl5iQS1","sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":19389,"input":19074,"output":228,"reasoning":87,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.005784489}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775897714149,"sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc09de20019oQFWSZdIn4MPE","messageID":"msg_d7bc091d900186194x2Wp0Ci1K","sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775897715865,"sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc0a010001egiG1BOs3W5zZ7","messageID":"msg_d7bc091d900186194x2Wp0Ci1K","sessionID":"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_e87177c83329471c9ff7384b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n2: \n3: **Module:** docs\n4: **Language:** TypeScript\n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube 项目建立基于 Docusaurus 3.x 的文档站点框架，集中管理项目的架构设计、API 参考、部署指南、开发手册和用户文档。当前项目文档散落在各模块的 `design.md`、`spec.md`、`README.md` 等文件中，缺乏统一的导航、搜索和版本管理能力。目标是提供一个可本地预览、可 CI 构建、可部署到 GitHub Pages 的结构化文档站，降低新贡献者的入门门槛，提升项目可维护性。\n10: \n11: ## Scope\n12: \n13: ### In Scope\n14: \n15: 1. **docs/ 目录初始化** — Docusaurus 3.x 项目脚手架\n16:    - `docusaurus.config.ts` — 站点配置（标题、URL、主题、插件）\n17:    - `sidebars.ts` — 侧边栏导航结构\n18:    - `package.json` — 依赖声明与脚本\n19:    - `tsconfig.json` — TypeScript 配置\n20:    - `babel.config.js` — Babel 配置（Docusaurus 要求）\n21: \n22: 2. **文档内容迁移与组织** — 将现有散落文档整合到 Docusaurus 结构中\n23:    - `docs/overview/` — 项目简介、架构概览、快速开始\n24:    - `docs/architecture/` — 各模块 design.md（router、workloadmanager、session-store、session-routing、sandbox-orchestration、deployment、ci-cd、code-execution、cli-toolkit、python-sdk、integrations、idle-cleanup）\n25:    - `docs/api/` — API 参考（workloadmanager REST API、client-go 库）\n26:    - `docs/guides/` — 部署指南、开发指南、贡献指南\n27:    - `docs/specs/` — 各模块 spec.md（规范文档）\n28: \n29: 3. **主题与样式**\n30:    - Infima 默认主题定制（AgentCube 品牌色、Logo）\n31:    - 代码块语法高亮（Go、Python、YAML、Bash、JSON）\n32:    - Mermaid 图表渲染支持（架构图、流程图）\n33:    - Admonition 组件使用规范（note、tip、warning、danger、info）\n34: \n35: 4. **插件与集成**\n36:    - `@docusaurus/plugin-content-docs` — 文档内容（内置）\n37:    - `@docusaurus/plugin-content-pages` — 独立页面（内置）\n38:    - `@docusaurus/theme-mermaid` — Mermaid 图表渲染\n39:    - `@docusaurus/plugin-ideal-image` — 图片优化（可选）\n40: \n41: 5. **构建与部署**\n42:    - `npm run start` — 本地开发服务器（热重载）\n43:    - `npm run build` — 生产构建\n44:    - `npm run deploy` — 部署到 GitHub Pages\n45:    - `.github/workflows/docs.yml` — CI 文档构建与部署 workflow\n46: \n47: 6. **Makefile 目标**\n48:    - `make docs-dev` — 启动本地文档开发服务器\n49:    - `make docs-build` — 构建生产版本文档\n50:    - `make docs-deploy` — 部署文档到 GitHub Pages\n51: \n52: ### Out of Scope\n53: \n54: - API 自动生成（Swagger/OpenAPI → 文档，后续单独 AR）\n55: - 多语言国际化（i18n），当前仅支持英文\n56: - 文档版本管理（v1.x、v2.x 等，后续按需添加）\n57: - 博客功能（Docusaurus blog plugin）\n58: - 搜索服务（Algolia DocSearch 配置，需申请 API key）\n59: - 修改任何生产代码（仅新增 docs/ 目录和相关配置）\n60: \n61: ## Architecture Summary\n62: \n63: ### Current State\n64: \n65: - 项目文档散落在各模块目录下：`router/design.md`、`deployment/spec.md`、`cli-toolkit/design.md` 等\n66: - `project.md` 提供项目级上下文，但无导航结构\n67: - 各模块 `changes/AR-XXX/proposal.md` 包含设计决策，但无法在线浏览\n68: - 无统一的文档站点，新贡献者需要手动翻阅多个文件理解项目\n69: - 无文档构建流程，无法预览文档渲染效果\n70: - `project.md` 中已明确技术栈包含 \"Docusaurus 3.x\"，但尚未落地\n71: \n72: ### Target State\n73: \n74: ```\n75: docs/\n76: ├── docusaurus.config.ts        # 站点配置\n77: ├── sidebars.ts                 # 侧边栏导航\n78: ├── package.json                # 依赖与脚本\n79: ├── tsconfig.json               # TypeScript 配置\n80: ├── babel.config.js             # Babel 配置\n81: ├── src/\n82: │   ├── css/\n83: │   │   └── custom.css          # 自定义样式\n84: │   └── pages/\n85: │       ├── index.tsx           # 首页\n86: │       └── markdown-page.md    # 示例页面\n87: ├── static/\n88: │   └── img/\n89: │       ├── logo.svg            # 项目 Logo\n90: │       └── favicon.ico         # 站点图标\n91: └── docs/\n92:     ├── overview/\n93:     │   ├── _category_.json\n94:     │   ├── introduction.md     # 项目简介（基于 project.md）\n95:     │   ├── architecture.md     # 架构概览\n96:     │   └── quick-start.md      # 快速开始\n97:     ├── architecture/\n98:     │   ├── _category_.json\n99:     │   ├── router.md           # Router 设计\n100:     │   ├── workloadmanager.md  # WorkloadManager 设计\n101:     │   ├── session-store.md    # Session Store 设计\n102:     │   ├── session-routing.md  # Session Routing 设计\n103:     │   ├── sandbox-orchestration.md\n104:     │   ├── deployment.md\n105:     │   ├── ci-cd.md\n106:     │   ├── code-execution.md\n107:     │   ├── cli-toolkit.md\n108:     │   ├── python-sdk.md\n109:     │   ├── integrations.md\n110:     │   └── idle-cleanup.md\n111:     ├── api/\n112:     │   ├── _category_.json\n113:     │   ├── workloadmanager-rest-api.md\n114:     │   └── client-go.md\n115:     ├── guides/\n116:     │   ├── _category_.json\n117:     │   ├── deployment-guide.md\n118:     │   ├── development-guide.md\n119:     │   └── contributing.md\n120:     └── specs/\n121:         ├── _category_.json\n122:         └── ...                 # 各模块 spec 文档\n123: ```\n124: \n125: **本地开发流程**：\n126: ```\n127: make docs-dev\n128:   → cd docs && npm install\n129:   → npx docusaurus start\n130:   → 浏览器打开 http://localhost:3000\n131:   → 编辑 .md 文件自动热重载\n132: ```\n133: \n134: **CI 构建流程**：\n135: ```\n136: .github/workflows/docs.yml\n137:   → push to main / PR\n138:   → npm install\n139:   → npm run build\n140:   → 验证构建成功\n141:   → (main only) deploy to GitHub Pages\n142: ```\n143: \n144: ## Impact Analysis\n145: \n146: ### Dependencies\n147: \n148: | 依赖 | 来源 | 说明 |\n149: |------|------|------|\n150: | Node.js 18+ | CI/本地环境 | Docusaurus 运行时要求 |\n151: | `@docusaurus/core` | npm 新增 | Docusaurus 核心框架（3.x） |\n152: | `@docusaurus/preset-classic` | npm 新增 | 经典预设（文档+博客+页面） |\n153: | `@docusaurus/theme-mermaid` | npm 新增 | Mermaid 图表渲染 |\n154: | `react` / `react-dom` | npm 新增 | Docusaurus UI 依赖（^18） |\n155: | `typescript` | npm 新增 | TypeScript 支持 |\n156: | GitHub Pages | GitHub | 文档托管目标 |\n157: \n158: ### Affected Components\n159: \n160: | 文件/目录 | 状态 | 说明 |\n161: |-----------|------|------|\n162: | `docs/` | 新增 | Docusaurus 项目根目录 |\n163: | `Makefile` | 修改 | 新增 `docs-dev`、`docs-build`、`docs-deploy` 目标 |\n164: | `.github/workflows/docs.yml` | 新增 | CI 文档构建与部署 workflow |\n165: | `.gitignore` | 修改 | 排除 `docs/node_modules/`、`docs/build/`、`docs/.docusaurus/` |\n166: | `docs/docs/overview/introduction.md` | 新增 | 基于 project.md 的项目简介 |\n167: | `docs/docs/architecture/*.md` | 新增 | 从各模块 design.md 迁移/引用 |\n168: \n169: ### Risk Assessment\n170: \n171: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n172: |------|------|----------|\n173: | Node.js 版本不匹配导致构建失败 | 中 | 在 workflow 中固定 Node.js 版本（20 LTS）；本地使用 .nvmrc |\n174: | 现有 design.md/spec.md 格式与 Docusaurus Markdown 不兼容 | 中 | 迁移时手动调整 frontmatter 和链接；保留原始文件作为 source of truth |\n175: | Mermaid 图表渲染性能问题（大图） | 低 | 限制单图复杂度；复杂图拆分为多个 |\n176: | 文档与代码不同步 | 中 | 在 PR 模板中增加\"文档是否更新\"检查项 |\n177: | GitHub Pages 部署权限问题 | 低 | 使用 GitHub Actions 内置 `GITHUB_TOKEN`；配置 Pages 部署权限 |\n178: | npm 依赖体积过大导致 CI 慢 | 低 | 使用 npm ci + 缓存 node_modules；Docusaurus 构建通常 <60s |\n179: \n180: ## Alternatives Considered\n181: \n182: ### 1. Docusaurus vs. MkDocs vs. Hugo（✅ 选定 Docusaurus）\n183: \n184: - **Docusaurus 3.x**：React 生态、TypeScript 原生支持、Mermaid 内置、GitHub Pages 部署简单、项目 tech stack 已指定\n185: - **MkDocs (Material)**：Python 生态、配置简单、但无 TypeScript 支持、与项目技术栈不一致\n186: - **Hugo**：构建速度极快、但主题定制复杂、学习曲线陡峭\n187: - **决策**：项目 project.md 已明确 \"Docs: Docusaurus 3.x\"，且团队熟悉 TypeScript/React，Docusaurus 是最自然的选择\n188: \n189: ### 2. 手动迁移文档 vs. 自动导入 vs. 保留原始文件+链接（✅ 选定混合策略）\n190: \n191: - **手动迁移**：复制内容到 docs/ 目录，调整格式，保持内容独立\n192: - **自动导入**：使用 Docusaurus 插件从外部路径读取 markdown\n193: - **保留原始+链接**：不复制，仅在文档站中提供链接指向原始文件\n194: - **决策**：项目简介和概览文档手动编写（基于 project.md）；架构文档从各模块 design.md 提取关键内容重新组织，原始文件保留作为 source of truth；使用 frontmatter `slug` 和 `custom_edit_url` 指向原始文件\n195: \n196: ### 3. 全文搜索：Algolia vs. 本地搜索 vs. 浏览器搜索（✅ 选定 Algolia DocSearch，暂用本地 fallback）\n197: \n198: - **Algolia DocSearch**：免费开源项目、搜索质量高、需申请 API key\n199: - **本地搜索插件**（@easyops-cn/docusaurus-search-local）：无需外部服务、搜索质量一般\n200: - **浏览器搜索**（Ctrl+F）：零配置、体验差\n201: - **决策**：初期使用 Docusaurus 内置搜索（基于页面标题和侧边栏），后续申请 Algolia DocSearch 替换\n202: \n203: ### 4. 文档与代码同仓库 vs. 独立仓库（✅ 选定同仓库）\n204: \n205: - **同仓库**：文档与代码版本同步、PR 可同时修改代码和文档、CI 统一\n206: - **独立仓库**：文档独立部署、但易与代码脱节、维护成本高\n207: - **决策**：文档与代码同仓库（`docs/` 目录），确保文档变更与代码变更在同一 PR 中审查\n208: \n209: ## Upstream Dependencies\n210: \n211: - 各模块 `design.md` 和 `spec.md` 文件内容稳定（作为文档来源）\n212: - `project.md` 作为项目简介的基础\n213: - GitHub 仓库已启用 GitHub Pages（需在 Settings 中配置）\n214: - Node.js 20 LTS 在 CI 环境中可用\n215: \n216: ## Test Strategy\n217: \n218: ### 验证方式\n219: \n220: 1. **本地预览验证**：`make docs-dev` 启动后，手动检查各页面渲染正确\n221: 2. **构建验证**：`make docs-build` 无错误、无 broken links\n222: 3. **CI 验证**：PR workflow 中运行 `npm run build`，失败则阻止合并\n223: 4. **链接检查**：使用 `@docusaurus/plugin-ideal-image` 或外部工具检查死链\n224: \n225: ### 文档质量标准\n226: \n227: | 检查项 | 标准 |\n228: |--------|------|\n229: | 构建成功 | `npm run build` 返回 0 |\n230: | 无 broken links | 所有内部链接可解析 |\n231: | Mermaid 渲染 | 所有 Mermaid 代码块正确渲染为图表 |\n232: | 代码高亮 | Go/Python/YAML/Bash/JSON 代码块语法高亮正确 |\n233: | 响应式布局 | 移动端/桌面端均可正常浏览 |\n234: | 侧边栏完整 | 所有文档在侧边栏中有对应入口 |\n235: \n236: ## Acceptance Criteria\n237: \n238: - [ ] `docs/` 目录包含完整的 Docusaurus 3.x 项目结构\n239: - [ ] `docusaurus.config.ts` 配置正确（标题、URL、主题、Mermaid 插件）\n240: - [ ] `sidebars.ts` 定义完整的文档导航结构（overview、architecture、api、guides、specs）\n241: - [ ] `package.json` 声明所有必要依赖（@docusaurus/core、preset-classic、theme-mermaid、react、react-dom、typescript）\n242: - [ ] `make docs-dev` 可启动本地开发服务器（http://localhost:3000）\n243: - [ ] `make docs-build` 可成功构建生产版本\n244: - [ ] `make docs-deploy` 可部署到 GitHub Pages\n245: - [ ] `.github/workflows/docs.yml` 在 PR 和 main push 时自动构建文档\n246: - [ ] `docs/docs/overview/introduction.md` 包含基于 project.md 的项目简介\n247: - [ ] `docs/docs/architecture/` 包含所有模块的设计文档入口\n248: - [ ] Mermaid 图表在文档站中正确渲染\n249: - [ ] 代码块支持 Go、Python、YAML、Bash、JSON 语法高亮\n250: - [ ] Admonition 组件（note、tip、warning、danger）可正常使用\n251: - [ ] 自定义样式（`custom.css`）应用 AgentCube 品牌色\n252: - [ ] `.gitignore` 排除 `docs/node_modules/`、`docs/build/`、`docs/.docusaurus/`\n253: - [ ] 不修改任何生产代码（仅新增 docs/ 目录、Makefile 目标、workflow）\n254: - [ ] 文档站首页（`src/pages/index.tsx`）包含项目简介和快速开始链接\n255: \n256: ## Status\n257: \n258: - [ ] Proposal review\n259: - [ ] Implementation\n260: - [ ] Verification\n\n(End of file - total 260 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n\n**Module:** docs\n**Language:** TypeScript\n**Size:** M\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube 项目建立基于 Docusaurus 3.x 的文档站点框架，集中管理项目的架构设计、API 参考、部署指南、开发手册和用户文档。当前项目文档散落在各模块的 `design.md`、`spec.md`、`README.md` 等文件中，缺乏统一的导航、搜索和版本管理能力。目标是提供一个可本地预览、可 CI 构建、可部署到 GitHub Pages 的结构化文档站，降低新贡献者的入门门槛，提升项目可维护性。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **docs/ 目录初始化** — Docusaurus 3.x 项目脚手架\n   - `docusaurus.config.ts` — 站点配置（标题、URL、主题、插件）\n   - `sidebars.ts` — 侧边栏导航结构\n   - `package.json` — 依赖声明与脚本\n   - `tsconfig.json` — TypeScript 配置\n   - `babel.config.js` — Babel 配置（Docusaurus 要求）","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775897715856,"end":1775897715863}}}}
